data.description: Cozy!  Original Hardwood Floors! NEW Roof! Freshly painted inside! Two updated bathrooms!  New tile flooring in the bathrooms, hallway, laundry and kitchen. Great kitchen with large dining area and hardwood floors throughout the living, dining and bedrooms. Enjoy the mornings in the best room of the house  - the spacious Sunroom. Lots of natural light and a cozy nook to relax and read a book.  Laundry is on the main level. Lots of storage.  The water heater is newer and the basement storage area is clean, and a great space to put all the extras.  This home is sold with the fridge, stove, detached garage, covered back porch area and a utility shed.  Downtown living, close to schools, restaurants, parks and more.
